                                         CAPE TOWN - A man has been arrested following a hostage drama in Mossel Bay. The situation unfolded on Sunday night after the suspect fired off a number of shots inside a house.  Police say the man was holding his parents hostage. He eventually let them go. Special task force members then stormed the house and overpowered him.